
          User Guide Notes



Overview

     The user guide will be split into two main sections: the user
documentation for the game, and for the level editing system.

     The game documentation will be written in the style of commercial
game documentation: that is, short and written in an easy to read style. 
Part of the game instructions will also be available to read from the game
itself (from a choice in the Options menu).

     The level editor documentation will, however, be written in a style
similar to commercial application: that is, more serious, in-depth and in
more of a reference manual style.


